definition: to toil/labor/laborer/to put sb to trouble (of doing sth)/meritorious deed/to console (Taiwan pr. [lao4] for this sense)
Slovakia/Slovak/abbr. for 斯洛伐克[Si1 luo4 fa2 ke4]

sentences.english: Laurence says he is ‘relaxed’ about increased demands for transparency.
sentences.chinese: 对于不断增长的透明要求，劳伦斯说他觉得“释然”。

sentences.english: And ships can reach the Atlantic Ocean from the Great Lakes through the Saint Lawrence Seaway.
sentences.chinese: 而船只则能够从五大湖经过圣劳伦斯航道到达大西洋。

sentences.english: Lawrence and Cissell could not be reached for comment.
sentences.chinese: 记者无法联系劳伦斯和西塞尔就此置评。

sentences.english: Lauren asked a bone-tired volunteer. The man shook his head.
sentences.chinese: 劳伦斯问一个累得筋疲力尽的自愿者，那人摇了摇头。

sentences.english: Lawrence Halprin was born in New York City in 1916.
sentences.chinese: 劳伦斯哈普林是在纽约市出生于1916年。

sentences.english: Elizabeth and Lawrence are chomping at the bit to go on vacation.
sentences.chinese: 伊莉莎白和劳伦斯迫不及待要去度假了。

sentences.english: Where's the lass and lobster Lanky Lawrence lost?
sentences.chinese: 兰基。劳伦斯失去了情妇和龙虾在哪里？

sentences.english: Lawrence, in his novels created 12 escapee images, who as an integrated whole serve the inherent connections and logical development.
sentences.chinese: 劳伦斯在他的小说中共塑造了12位出逃者的形象。

sentences.english: Did Lanky Lawrence lose his lass and lobster?
sentences.chinese: 兰基。劳伦斯失去了他的情妇和龙虾吗？

sentences.english: She was disappointed by what Lawrence said.
sentences.chinese: 她对劳伦斯说的话感到失望。

sentences.english: You meet a man called Lawrence at a dinner party.
sentences.chinese: 你在晚宴上遇到一个叫劳伦斯的人。

sentences.english: Lady Chatterley's Lover is the most controversial works by Lawrence.
sentences.chinese: 《查太莱夫人的情人》是劳伦斯一生最受诟议的著作。

sentences.english: But Lawrence's statement implies far more than this, both morally and artistically.
sentences.chinese: 但无论道德上，还是艺术上，劳伦斯的描述不止于此。

sentences.english: This year marks the fiftieth anniversary of the seaway's opening.
sentences.chinese: 今年是圣劳伦斯航道开通的五十周年。

sentences.english: Passion runs through lawrence's works, in which human instinct predominates.
sentences.chinese: 劳伦斯的作品流淌的是激情，推崇的是人的本性。

sentences.english: Tony Leung Chiu Wai (the one who's been in a bunch of Wong Kar Wai movies, not Tony Leung Ka Fai) is a big fan of American crime writer Lawrence Block.
sentences.chinese: 梁朝伟是美国犯罪作家劳伦斯卜洛克的大粉丝。

definition: Michel or Mitchell (name)/George Mitchell (1933-), US Democratic party politician and diplomat, influential in brokering Northern Ireland peace deal in 1990s, US Middle East special envoy from 2009
Hailun county level city in Suihua 綏化|绥化, Heilongjiang/Helen or Hélène (name)
